properties.areaDesc: Whitefish Bay (U.S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point Iroquois MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 8 at 2:51PM EST until January 9 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds 20 to 30 knots with gusts up to 40 knots
and seas 4 to 6 ft expected.

* WHERE...Whitefish Bay (U. S. Portion)/Whitefish Point to Point
Iroquois MI.

* WHEN...From 11 AM to 7 PM EST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 11 AM TO 7 PM EST THURSDAY
